title: tKOI

title: Export Gene Exploration Data — export_gene_exploration_data
text: function performs following steps: Merges expression_data tKOIList object gene metadata using inner_join. Merges result gene-level network data using right_join. Selects key columns merged dataset, including: gene_name: Gene names experimental data. name: Gene symbols common names. id identifier: Unique identifiers genes network. logfc: Experimental log fold change values. pvalue: Experimental p-values. pagerank: tKOI PageRank scores. beta: tKOI z-scores network enrichment. p_value: tKOI unadjusted p-values. fdr: tKOI false discovery rates (FDR). Renames columns clarity standardization.
